! Delinea Platform Network Requirements
! Generated by delinea-netconfig
!
!
! Outbound Rules (Egress)
ip access-list extended DELINEA-OUTBOUND
 remark platform - Platform services for <tenant> (hostname: <tenant>.delinea.app, portal.<tenant>.delinea.app)
 remark secret_server - Secret Server Cloud endpoints for <tenant> (hostname: <tenant>.secretservercloud.com, api.<tenant>.secretservercloud.com, app.<tenant>.secretservercloud.com)
 10 remark static_service - Static service without tenant placeholders
 11 permit tcp any 199.83.128.0 0.0.7.255 eq 443
 20 remark static_service - Static service without tenant placeholders
 21 permit tcp any 198.143.32.0 0.0.31.255 eq 443
!
! Inbound Rules (Ingress)
ip access-list extended DELINEA-INBOUND
 10 remark webhooks - Webhook endpoints from <tenant>
 11 permit tcp 13.68.202.64 0.0.0.7 any eq 443
!
! End of ACL
